v25.3.24 Update Notes:

This update adds MTProto proxy for Telegram

New Features:
1. MTProto proxy for Telegram via Docker (menu item 20)
2. Auto-install Docker if not present
3. Port selection with conflict detection (default 443)
4. Fake TLS domain selection (google.com, cloudflare.com, microsoft.com, apple.com, amazon.com, github.com, or custom)
5. Auto-generated secret key (16-byte hex)
6. Full Alpine Linux support (OpenRC)
7. tg://proxy link for one-click Telegram configuration

See: https://github.com/anyagixx/proxme3
